{"type": "article", "id": 48585, "title": "这组以岛屿为灵感的沙发，圆润得惊人｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-25T23:07:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 46550, "name": "Appree"}, {"id": 15823, "name": "&tradition"}, {"id": 46551, "name": "Nimio"}, {"id": 46552, "name": "Mike Simonelli"}, {"id": 8928, "name": "Luca Nichetto"}, {"id": 46553, "name": "Ryo Yamazaki"}, {"id": 46554, "name": "Leonardo Betti"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 182, "image": "img/article/article_show/201712251710337xFtCDZVNyn1YbUI.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: #222222} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: #222222} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #222222} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #222222; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #222222} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Albers Numbers by Leonardo Betti</h3><p>Albers Numbers 是数字艺术家 Leonardo Betti 推出的最新项目，赋予其灵感的，是 20 世纪最具影响力的艺术家之一 Josef Albers。这个项目包括 9 个与版式相关的色彩实验作品。Betti 对 Albers 作品中的色彩运用极为感兴趣，那种介入传统欧洲艺术和新美国艺术之间的表达激发了他的创作欲。</p><p>“我的目的是专注于色彩交叠时色彩渐变的感觉，因此我选择了树脂玻璃材质，” Betti 解释道。每个数字艺术作品都由多层彩色树脂玻璃层构成，唤起一种充满深度与情绪的私密感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171158orZiX5EaeL6CUwN4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171158P2VC0BKDAe3F8vmt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171159KSJig7VvEeuP3Aqw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171159umpcLrBF0M3VHCzT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171159cMNgDAYHz2dQ6JqC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171200AvKfslLghSwpJxqB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/leonardoworx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cats In Hats Made From Their Own Hair by Ryo Yamazaki</h3><p>一千个猫奴，面对家里随处可见的猫毛，大概会有一千种情绪。但日本摄影师 Ryo Yamazaki 却从猫毛中挖掘出了创意。猫毛在他手中变成了猫帽，尤其是一款光滑整洁的傻瓜锥形猫帽，引发了不小的关注度。之后，包括特朗普的额前发、莱娅公主假发以及古怪的巫师帽等各种形态的帽子被制作出来，试图展现潮流趋势。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171248uLjOU1GPbTY6dtrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171248Q3suGe5ZpSyhaoNJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171249SJrPTbzHFnvZKiQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171249Zu5gKdJOocWtnl6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171249UNaXbpGBAt39CLgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171250AVGXe70R9uHkhn6F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171252vO7y1K9jpJboZfFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712251712560aDsvSAGIBeMrzqL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/these-cat-hair-cat-hats-are-going-viral-not-to-be-mistaken-for-diors-fw17-beret-12-21-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hanami Coffee Tables by Nimio</h3><p>Nimio 是一个设计和生产日用家居用品和手工物品的实验室，其推出的新系列 Hanami 是一组咖啡桌。Hanami 是一种日本传统的赏花习俗，比如观赏梅花、樱花，或在盛开的樱花树下宴饮庆祝。</p><p>Nimio 设计的这组小桌不只限定在咖啡桌功能，也可以用于摆放植物、玩具，做杂志桌或是独独成一个装饰元素。不同的高度，表面是六角马赛克砖的样式，有一种淡淡的地中海风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171335hpDznLWoglmAV6wC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171335qX8E6s7vy1OKA9uF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.688889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171335vCI4Ow1NTe8a0xrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171336nOw0HatFB9s7kVLA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171336MwjB45cGtpQabz9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171336by02NifjOVhM3mWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nimio-lab.es/en/hanami-i\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nimio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Isole Modular Seating by Luca Nichetto and Nendo for &amp;tradition</h3><p>意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 联手日本设计工作室 Nendo 的创始人 Oki Sato，为丹麦设计品牌 &amp;tradition 设计了一款名为 Isole 的沙发。这是一个模块化沙发系统，两个高产的设计师以“岛屿”为主题设计了这款造型独特的沙发。</p><p>Isole 的特点是圆润造型的垫子搁在粉末涂层的底座上，每个座椅之间留下一点空间。用户可以选择不同的配置，包括有没有扶手的座椅，或是搭配的或是圆形或是方形或是矩形的边桌，提供单人座、双人座以及三人座的尺寸和四种颜色的选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171524khS8dgKQRexzJinl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712251714545ebtkgdTF81WrKfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171454cVMg2xlHPEraQiLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171428aImM0CiWRsyVSGug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712251714294FYCWiMLqKnezoQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551562\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171429vaXlDSLcB5bnHpQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171429VTXI4gqfB7KsmlWt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.467969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171429EYyqUlkDKui9thxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.432813\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/isole-modular-seating-by-luca-nichetto-and-nendo-for-tradition/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171430Wny673JfTFKZEQdP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The OClock by Mike Simonelli</h3><p>OClock 挂钟是今年红点设计概念大奖的得奖作品，出自设计师 Mike Simonelli 之手。它颠覆了传统时钟的报时方式，不仅仅没有时针分针，更特别的是，它是以表盘的转动来显示时间的。表盘是一个圆形的金属圈，上面均匀分布了60个小齿槽，每一个齿槽的移动代表一分钟，外侧带有12个数字。上部正中的指针带有一个小齿轮，时钟以表盘与小齿轮咬合转动的方式来显示时间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171634NIBKeqpCMYTnG0W7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171634hIEtM7l9oCbFHwOi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171600uOoDENXjid5CwnFp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171602SpdUEmtMCsWPjgZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171602OA4b6Tqv7wRg3FcZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171602v4wR5M27TU1FyczZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2017/12/21/from-oclock-to-whoaclock/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Leaf Magnet by Appree</h3><p>这是韩国设计工作室 Appree 的作品，一系列橡胶磁力贴，设计师将其做成各种自然形状，比如银杏叶、枫叶、樱花、贝壳灯形状，保持了天然材料本身的美感。它可以用于各种场所，包括隔断、白板、冰箱等。套装售价 10 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/margnet-appree-11-23-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171811i0pb8J9EcGCyKDgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171743V6TYhgEQMFkG3wPu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712251717440BQVOecKnIHX471C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712251717449D2TLsmfPiGqFA6O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171742MbjOKalIL6xWr3zB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171225171745b413yY8iftdwUMNH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}